N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1ยง 1.6 - Method of determining vitamin D content

State Regulations

In determining the vitamin D level of milk, such approved
laboratories shall use a method prescribed in the latest edition of Official

Methods of Analysis published by the Association of Official Agricultural

Chemists, or by such modified method as may be approved by the
commissioner. Notes
